# Keep the build context clean + reproducible: never ship host artifacts into
# the image. node_modules is installed inside the Dockerfile, so host copies
# must not leak in (they masked a missing-deps bug on clean checkouts).
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/target
**/.turbo
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/.DS_Store

# Env + secrets (never build into an image)
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# VCS / tooling
.git
.github
**/gen
dist-updater
